cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Orcha in your research or build on it, please cite it as below."
title: "Orcha: Human-authoritative multi-agent orchestration"
abstract: >-
  Orcha coordinates multiple Claude Code agents on a shared objective through a
  Postgres-backed coordination layer, with a human holding standing authority
  (approve, reprioritise, reassign, arbitrate) over every subtask.
type: software
